budget

Class Attachment

  • java.lang.Object
    • budget.Attachment

  • public class Attachment
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a file that is added at the end of the budget when it is printed. It provides methods to get the file using classes in package dao and storage.
    Author:
    oscar
